{"tid":2074221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子誤信治便秘偏方 竟塞活黃鱔入肛門 on.cc 東網 on.cc 東網\t 23.5k 人追蹤","createTime":"2020-06-22T02:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T04:02:27.000Z","uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"36754b2d0a6e16008b6a11779f89926aa11247b2","tid":2074221,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"廣東東莞一名男子近日腹脹、腹痛難耐入院治療，更出現感染性休克。經腹部CT檢查，醫生懷疑他腹腔有異物，隨後進行腹腔鏡探查後，竟發現男子腹中異物是一條黃鱔。原來，<span style=\"color: red;\">該男子便秘已久，想起坊間有傳黃鱔可通便，於是買了一條活黃鱔塞進肛門。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子到院時表示，自己已經腹脹一周，腹痛近5小時。當時他血壓下降，表現為感染性休克，已無法與人正常交流。<span style=\"color: red;\">醫生根據症狀，結合腹部CT檢查，判斷他消化道穿孔，之後用腹腔鏡探查驚訝地發現黃鱔。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據指，<span style=\"color: red;\">黃鱔進入了男子整個腹腔後已死亡，而事主的腹腔污染嚴重，伴有大量淡綠色的滲液，腹壁、腸道、肝臟等多處亦附有膿苔和糞便</span>，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醫生遂確定他乙狀結腸破裂。最終經開刀，長約40厘米的黃鱔終得以取出。據已康復出院的事主指，黃鱔是從市場購買，誰知塞進肛門後便秘不僅沒有緩解，反而更痛，因此才到院處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NJLAY9Rmst6dnl12k2ZEpQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-06/d97f9900-b421-11ea-bf97-49224ebc91ea\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNJLAY9Rmst6dnl12k2ZEpQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-06%2Fd97f9900-b421-11ea-bf97-49224ebc91ea&h=8cd49ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca2de22d0de4ea22d8371f7d888a3a7db57dbec","tid":2074221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加咗生動D?"},{"pid":"13afc813c4c81100304ef391f2b57516c8c8c4b6","tid":2074221,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=q3i83j/ctp-vzntr/9qqqss0371o8439nnq38322q832r2766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dq3i83j%2Fctp-vzntr%2F9qqqss0371o8439nnq38322q832r2766.jpg&h=fa576470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn20190826ac/176/w585h391/20190826/e1bd-icuacrz6915855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinacn20190826ac%2F176%2Fw585h391%2F20190826%2Fe1bd-icuacrz6915855.jpg&h=a16b089c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=q3i83j/ctp-vzntr/9qqqss0371o8439nnq38322q832r2766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dq3i83j%2Fctp-vzntr%2F9qqqss0371o8439nnq38322q832r2766.jpg&h=fa576470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843d9823b038166f274a26d2f147de2aefb10466","tid":2074221,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ca2de22d0de4ea22d8371f7d888a3a7db57dbec","tid":2074221,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加咗生動D?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eb6f90f23db6